Class SEScriptEngine

java.lang.Object
javax.script.AbstractScriptEngine
ca.cgjennings.apps.arkham.plugins.SEScriptEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilable, Invocable, ScriptEngine
public final class SEScriptEngine extends AbstractScriptEngine implements Invocable, Compilable
Implementation of ScriptEngine for the modified Mozilla Rhino build used for Strange Eons scripts.
